  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d0d84746-429f-4b54-b784-a99710c54404\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ab2031cd-4328-4ccb-8598-3e9b5793483f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-283d8940-26d3-4f5e-bc3b-19f127f01fb6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96c2bf0a-7f9e-444f-a2f1-5e7dcd59d8f5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-96c2bf0a-7f9e-444f-a2f1-5e7dcd59d8f5\", \"src\" : \"https://max-website20-images.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/shoulder_pain_what_could_be_reason_1_8273180275.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"6000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3375\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://max-website20-images.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/shoulder_pain_what_could_be_reason_1_8273180275.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a4f9f335-a3f7-42ab-aa11-16ff38703930\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6c45be93-5621-42ea-9582-a28abb552bb1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6697675a-5f9a-4a2c-bf53-bf25c0385b94\">이 부위 아픈 분들이 많습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2617cf78-1eed-402b-9555-527dad5b45b5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2151d483-3282-40c3-a91b-1b749da30a54\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-82fa3a4b-9529-4595-8fb9-830f016e331f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ddf67db4-8be0-4466-9fd2-0c3a93d690bc\">뻐근하다</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-72a7586f-ac43-4213-b61e-b24d39cdb906\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-86a6a5f4-5041-4034-bee2-3bf26914f9ce\">무겁다</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c13531e2-b259-4208-b7f7-93efbc5f1a5d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a93fcccb-e0f8-41cf-8970-018508a67dfa\">아침에 일어났는데 목이 안돌아가고 너무 아프다</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-94ffceab-922f-4f14-aabe-6064b1ce524a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b0828e65-9094-4673-bade-0592e9e0a8c7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cd40571c-16e6-424e-a5ca-41637a7bad8c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-df990ed8-07ee-424f-a433-729e89af8a5a\">제각기 표현은 다르지만 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4a7a2029-08c3-4504-bcd4-a2dc2500e241\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b3a868ff-2179-4d20-91f7-64655eda8849\">아픈 부위는 붉게 표시된 부위고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a9c659ac-c004-4e8d-84c0-a021b0781a17\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aa32946e-35b3-4cd5-9131-c7392e19f0cd\">&#x27;어깨가 아프다&#x27;고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-987ee13b-0858-4eed-946c-ad2a9497b692\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a6cc8e3b-2a6d-46f1-a1e2-c72275621ba8\">(어깨가 아프다고 하면 저 부위인지, 어깨 관절인지 부터 구분해야 해요)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cc289c91-2962-44af-8a8e-f6d88f731522\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5ee488f1-e854-49f0-98a5-b79836a2ae27\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-437f2b9a-e8f2-4f6d-a922-09b6737a1336\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-101c7314-6c20-43ea-9f59-5b01a9345416\">단순한 근육 뭉침일 수도 있고, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b664210d-9dc0-4c55-a902-28b16b7cf5f6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-770ed8f7-d062-4a9d-a308-d72c1d0e930c\">신경 눌림에 의한 통증일 수도 있고, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c78d493f-8781-47e3-abc1-5a8fd9167f7d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4d3ea850-8a7f-40e1-9ade-358d38bb4478\">목 디스크로 인한 증상일 수도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bc93b53f-eacc-4a59-9c71-f1d9dc56b32a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3725811c-19e3-4086-bcef-b6cf8a0679ac\">물론  다른 원인일 수도 있지요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-32924f7d-6d15-40ce-acbd-bc0301de5530\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0ca4d41d-c965-4613-998c-274dee168454\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-57f0e9f5-b4ec-471f-a8b2-c74e16c0fb4a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dd345689-45d7-4c9a-bf53-90edcb6b3c97\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-91150137-db22-42e6-be19-9850c2f47afb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:375px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-91150137-db22-42e6-be19-9850c2f47afb\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6f5ff8114cc559a9.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"375\", \"originalHeight\" : \"268\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6f5ff8114cc559a9.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6f5ff8114cc559a9.png\" data-width=\"375\" data-height=\"268\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1617e8e5-c6d4-4785-baf6-512cd0ecfdad\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a5aeeff-03a3-46a6-9bbc-9c49b36d49d9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3f7c4b43-6c9f-45df-b757-4b0e9870f7c0\">위 그림의 노란색으로 칠해진게 신경(nerve)입니다. 신경은 신체기능이 정상적으로 유지되기 위해 반드시 필요한 구조물이죠. 그리고 눌리는 압박이나 당겨지는 신장력 등에 의해서 손상받기가 쉽습니다. 신경통, 신경손상, 디스크로 인한 신경증상 등등.. 신경과 관련된 병이 많죠</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ccf73dbd-042e-461a-b554-37f4330a19a0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-51292dd2-1739-4a83-9270-500b6edb4dbc\">그래서 노란색 신경을 보호하기 위해 마치 갑옷처럼 회색의 막이 신경을 둘러싸고 있습니다. 회색으로 표현된 이 두텁고 질긴 막을 경막(dura)이라 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7000ec0b-7e15-464b-b1e0-a389688ff8fb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7b02439c-37e8-4479-93a9-057ad76a91bb\">디스크가 신경쪽으로 튀어나오게 되면, 신경을 누르기 전에 경막(dura)을 먼저 건드리게 되겠죠? 경막이 건드려지면 통증이 생기는데 이를 경막통증(dural pain)이라 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-272c7297-e922-4461-badd-989a9a467ad5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:333px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-272c7297-e922-4461-badd-989a9a467ad5\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f6ea51b350d43cbb.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"333\", \"originalHeight\" : \"310\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f6ea51b350d43cbb.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f6ea51b350d43cbb.png\" data-width=\"333\" data-height=\"310\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1c4a1ade-2104-4890-b7be-cb3c892267fa\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-412dc355-e88c-47d7-b638-86435c8f46a1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-603f6717-12cc-4567-b50a-70015468e616\">경막이 C2-3(경추 2번 3번 사이)에서 눌리면 뒷통수부위에 통증이 생기고, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7b7dd766-6741-4d55-b2af-e83312455de3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-912d97cf-6a49-4803-b06f-cb53d4d4ac3c\">경막이 C5-6(경추 5번 6번 사이)에서 눌리면 어깨라인 위쪽으로 통증이 생긴다는 걸 표시한 겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cddf1e51-0fcc-4ef8-a82f-be7b8201ea01\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-86c90783-917d-4ac3-8ddd-690ec4438231\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f990dcd5-ec9d-4039-8c5a-fc8c359a8741\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:476px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f990dcd5-ec9d-4039-8c5a-fc8c359a8741\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c816fa7d2de08fe2.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"476\", \"originalHeight\" : \"346\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c816fa7d2de08fe2.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c816fa7d2de08fe2.png\" data-width=\"476\" data-height=\"346\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6d2a7444-9cbc-413c-9e39-421b0bab32e5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:436px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6d2a7444-9cbc-413c-9e39-421b0bab32e5\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b66bb91bb88c9de7.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"436\", \"originalHeight\" : \"344\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b66bb91bb88c9de7.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b66bb91bb88c9de7.png\" data-width=\"436\" data-height=\"344\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4b2cc22f-89be-473b-a628-9d6daeea4baf\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-261e44f3-61cb-4e4b-bfe6-da92503b6938\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-483b25f7-ad53-4141-8110-666f37f75815\">어깨부위에 통증을 유발하는 대표적인 근육 두 가지 입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-52b4fb53-99a3-4212-a34b-276fcfdba7cb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ffd49e98-88cb-49b1-88c3-a18c32e7a624\">위는 견갑거근.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6d329727-6fd3-4c29-8201-4271d86f23f1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3ca10051-7138-4524-82fa-ae4ee0e9d001\">아래는 승모근.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6b82e053-3557-4643-ba8a-1a0e997bf4f5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ee39c082-cca8-4d64-a450-79144cba0652\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6c1316a8-d93b-4524-9f57-a9e626877bd8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5e9270da-fa1b-4156-a89a-d30ef0dd2560\">근육 뭉침에 의해서도 어깨 윗 라인에 통증이 생길 수 있죠</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-318d243a-de82-43ee-856a-4142eefe91ad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-306bddad-4bae-4cc6-a43b-54e6ed633c5c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-77a84bed-a1bc-46ec-8ff1-c87adac5e7c1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-07d8436c-4bd6-4803-9ed4-afb8a73a74e8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96b3277c-61b7-4c61-9c48-7a36dddb875b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-